question: Tī chit kho͘ hē-lia̍t sè-kài tńg-chiap tang-tiong, ū siáng-gîn chhú-tit choân tn̂g chē pái tē-it ūi? (Tī chit kho͘ hē-lia̍t liân-sai-á lāi, ū siáng-gîn chhú-tit siōng chē pái tē-it ūi? )
McLaren - Honda chit ê Constructor tit-to-to-la̍k koaiñ?
Tui Rocky-te Grand Prix, Rocky-te lap si Jonathan Palmer, chiah-chúi constructor iâⁿ?
Tui Ferrara chit ke constructor, tī sai-lāi-lāi ê chiuⁿ-chiuⁿ, te̍k-pia̍t sī tùi Hông-gâ-lī Grand Prix (Rd. 10) chiah khai-sí, in ê cheng-cheng thiau-tiâu sī cháiⁿ-iūⁿ?
answer: Tī sai-lāi-lāi ê chiuⁿ-chiuⁿ, Ferrara hián-bī chhut kiông-tāi ê cheng-cheng-la̍t, m̄-koh bē-tàng kóng sī chha-put-to hiah-ê sî-chūn lóng ū kiông-tāi. Tī Hông-gâ-lī Grand Prix (Rd. 10) in tit-tio̍h chi̍t pái sèng-lī, sī Nigel Mansell tit-tio̍h, koh tī Phû-tô-gâ Grand Prix (Rd. 13) sī Gerhard Berger tit-tio̍h. In mā tit-tio̍h nn̄g pái Mansell ê tē-it khoai chhiau-sok kap tī Hông-gâ-lī ê Berger ê tóng-iú Riccardo Patrese tit-tio̍h ê tē-it lí khui-chhia-tiâⁿ. Tī chiah-ê te̍k-pia̍t sî-chūn chi-gōa, in bē-tàng tit-tio̍h hit kui-ê sî-kî ê pa̍h-gōa pái pí-sài, in ê pa̍h-gōa pái pí-sài lóng sī McLaren-Honda ia̍h-sī Benetton-Ford tit-tio̍h. Che piáu-bī, Ferrara sī ū cheng-cheng-la̍t, m̄-koh bē-tàng kóng sī tōa-thâu.

question: Chiu chiah ê Grand Prix, tùi chū-tōa-chōa (pole position) ê kiû-chhia-chhiú hōan-būn sī iâⁿ-chiáⁿ, ū siáⁿ-chiah? (List the Grand Prix races where the driver who secured pole position was not the same driver who won the race.)
Ferarri Constructor 赢若干个 比/赛？

Jī-ê-ê sū-kiāⁿ tī July goe̍h kí-hêng, ài kiám-cha chhú-siau iâⁿ-chiáⁿ, chi̍t-ê siōng-kúi-ê hòan-chhia ê jîn-bu̍t thè-thiàm chiâⁿ iâⁿ-chiáⁿ, Tiong-kok Tāi-chióng-sài ê sin ê kiàⁿ-chō-chiáⁿ sī siáⁿ-mi̍h?
Oaⁿ-lâi ê chu-liāu lâi mn̄g, tit-tio̍h siāng kín ê tôaⁿ chhia kap tit-tio̍h chiàn-iâⁿ ê koan-hē sī siáⁿ-khoán?
answer: Ūi-tio̍h-tio̍h 15 tiâu chū-sài, ū 4 tiâu chū-sài sī iâⁿ ê chú-sài mā tit-tio̍h siāng kín ê tôaⁿ chhia (Ayrton Senna tī San Marino, Ji̍t-pún, kap Se-pa-liâ Grand Prix, chiū-chāi Alain Prost tī Hoat-kok Grand Prix). Che ì-sù sī kóng tī 15 tiâu chū-sài tang-lâi ê 11 tiâu (chiap-kīn 73%), iâⁿ ê chú-sài bô sī siāng kín ê tôaⁿ chhia ê chú-sài, chū-án-ne chhut-khí lâi kóng, choân-tâi ê chū-sài sok-tō͘ kap kò͘-ōe khah tiōng-iàu jiân-āu tit-tio̍h iâⁿ, pí-kàu kòe chi̍t ê siāng kín ê sok-tō͘ ê sî-chūn khah tiōng-iàu.

question: It-ê phoe-á lāi-bīn ū siáⁿ-chióng lūi ê chū-liāu, hō͘-chòe, kài-sò͘ ê sū-kiāⁿ lóng bô-kâng-sè ê lūi ê chū-liāu?
Si ê constructors ná-sé ài chiam-chòe tiām-chāi--ê, teh chiap-chhiú chi̍t ê pí-sài lóng thàn chiah-ê?
Pai-siong ê Grand Prix ū A-ia̍h Senna tek ti̍h pole, tān-sī Lâi-ket Mânsell tit tio̍h koàⁿ?
answer: Brazil Grand Prix, chāi-lāi A-ia̍h Senna chiap pole, lâi Lâi-ket Mânsell tit tio̍h, kó͘-sū chē-chē sū-kiāⁿ bē-tàng chòe-chōe-ê sū-kiāⁿ hō͘ sū-kiāⁿ kap chè-tō͘ éng-hióng chiâⁿ-chòe.
